PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776255072
OL,3,CSunderland condemn online racist abuse
OL,4,Cof Brian Brobbey after Tottenham game
OL,6,FThe statement added: "This is not an
OL,7,Fisolated incident, recent abuse
OL,8,Fdirected at Romaine Mundle and
OL,9,FLutsharel Geertruida highlights the
OL,10,Fongoing and unacceptable frequency of
OL,11,Fthis behaviour, both inside stadiums
OL,12,Fand online.
OL,14,F"The club has reported this incident
OL,15,Fto the Premier League, the relevant
OL,16,Fsocial media platforms and the police,
OL,17,Fand we expect swift action to be taken
OL,18,Fagainst those responsible.
OL,26,@nD@VOUvD@AOU
