PN,42904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776255072
OL,3,CSunderland condemn online racist abuse
OL,4,Cof Brian Brobbey after Tottenham game
OL,6,F"Racism is abhorrent and has no place
OL,7,Fin our game or in society, and we will
OL,8,Fcontinue to call it out clearly and
OL,9,Funapologetically every time it occurs.
OL,11,F"Football must be a safe and inclusive
OL,12,Fenvironment for all ` without
OL,13,Fexception."
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
